Cheats to be typed in on the cheatmenu are:-
--------------------------------------------
what the hell is this        -         An advert for #amigames, accompanied by some music :)
widdy                        -         Me as a pet.  A bit vain, really.
rick                         -         Rick from #amigames as a pet.
buffalo                      -         A buffalo as a pet.
donkey follower              -         Andy Davidson as a pet.
evolve                       -         The pet evolves.
donkey                       -         A pointless cheat that wasn't worth putting in the game.
