other hints.....

-When your pet is ill, treat him immediately.  He will get unhappy very quickly if you don't.
-Keep an eye on your pet's weight by clicking the info button.  Make sure his weight is between
 20 and 40 on the graph.  Believe me, it will make life easier for you.
-Make your pet as happy as possible.  This will make less work in the future for you.
 